messages.message:
Two small copyedits for deployment metrics:
1. Can we change the *Configure threshold* button to *Configure alerts* ? This is a more accurate description of what you're doing there, and we use "threshold" already to mean something different. 
2. Can we change all instances of *A/average* to *A/avg* (no period) ? I count 6 of these on the page. For accuracy metrics, we went with Avg/avg in all cases, so we should do the same here. 
@Liam Callanan @jack.robbins
